&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Demand Generation and Campaign Manager &lt;/strong&gt;at TimescaleüêØ, you will play a crucial role in supporting the development and execution of marketing strategies aimed at attracting, nurturing, and converting potential customers into qualified leads and building excitement and engagement with technical communities. Working closely with the Senior Manager, you will help drive campaigns, analyze performance data, and optimize marketing efforts to achieve company goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Top candidates will thrive in a fast-paced environment and enjoy the challenge of taking full ownership and responsibility for driving high-quality leads and signups. An exceptional, demonstrable use of an experimental mindset and business insights to drive results and ROI is necessary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in setting strategies, goals, and forecasts for demand generation, nurture, and campaigns in alignment with sales and marketing objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan and execute multi-channel sales and marketing campaigns, including email marketing, landing pages, paid advertisements, events, and webinars.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and analyze marketing/sales metrics and campaign performance to make data-driven decisions and optimizations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally to create and manage content assets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize marketing automation tools such as HubSpot and Salesforce to manage lead data and workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the effective use of the marketing tech stack, ensuring tools are utilized efficiently and effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct competitive and market analysis to inform campaign strategies and improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in B2B SaaS marketing, with a focus on lead generation and campaign execution.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in using HubSpot and Salesforce for marketing automation and lead management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in managing paid ad campaigns, particularly on platforms such as Google Ads and LinkedIn.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills with the ability to interpret data and make data-driven decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent organizational, communication, and project management skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently and collaboratively in a fast-paced, remote environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enthusiasm for learning and applying new marketing strategies and technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Preferred Skills:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with database and/or cloud products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with technical audiences and AI products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with developer channels and newsletters (ex: Hacker News, dev.to, PG Weekly).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creative problem-solving abilities and a proactive mindset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong writing and editing skills for creating compelling marketing content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;By applying for this position, you are agreeing to &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.timescale.com/legal/timescale-applicant-privacy-notice&quot;&gt;Timescale&#39;s Applicant Privacy Notice.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 900;&quot;&gt;Work from anywhere, impact everywhere&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Diversity is at the heart of who we are at Xapo Bank. We‚Äôre a fully distributed team of over 140 Xapiens that work remotely from 40+ countries around the world.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our beginning: A world that enjoys economic freedom and wealth protection, no matter where you live or who is running your country. This is the dream that drove Wences Casares, our Founder and Chairman, to quietly transform the world of banking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To achieve that, we search the world for the best people for the job. We work hard, think globally, and inspire each other to learn and grow. We are committed to changing the way things are done.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Risk is inherent in all of our business activities and managing risk well is the responsibility of every Xapien. Sound risk management enables us to serve our customers and deliver value for our shareholders, and helps make Xapo a great place to work.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;Although we are headquartered in Gibraltar, this is a full time, 100% remote position&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;Work from anywhere!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Position overview&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Head of Content Marketing, reporting into the VP of Marketing, will play a crucial role in developing and executing Xapo Bank‚Äôs content strategy to drive brand awareness, engagement, and ultimately, conversions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement a comprehensive content marketing strategy that aligns with the company‚Äôs growth objectives and brand positioning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead SEO efforts to increase visibility and organic search rankings, collaborating closely with web developers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage content production across various formats including blogs, white papers, video, and social media, ensuring all content is on-brand, consistent in terms of style, quality, and tone of voice, and optimized for search and user experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the editorial calendar and ensure content is scheduled, produced, and published in a timely manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze content marketing data and SEO performance to continually refine strategies and tactics, maximizing effectiveness and ROI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the content and design for Xapo Bank&#39;s website&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams, including product, PR, and digital marketing, to create synergies and leverage content across all channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and expand the content marketing team, nurturing talent and developing skills to meet evolving market and organizational demands.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster relationships with key influencers, thought leaders, and external partners to amplify outreach and content distribution efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current with industry trends and competitor strategies to ensure that our content is ahead of the curve.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Skills needed&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least 10 years of experience in a similar role spanning content and organic marketing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor‚Äôs degree in Marketing, Communications, Journalism, or a related field. Advanced degree preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience in content marketing and SEO, with a strong track record of enhancing organic search and engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills with an ability to interpret data to make informed content decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional writing and editing skills, with a keen understanding of what resonates with target audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with content management systems, SEO tools (e.g., SEMrush, Ahrefs), and analytics platforms (e.g., Google Analytics).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Other requirements&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated workspace.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A reliable internet connection with the fastest speed possible in your area.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Devices and other essential equipment that meet minimal technical specifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Alignment with Our Values and the Xapo Values-Driven Leadership principles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why work for Xapo?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
