&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Enhanced Data Analysis and Financial Modeling:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;Advanced statistical and mathematical expertise to our team. This will enable us to develop more sophisticated financial models, improve the accuracy of our forecasts, and provide deeper insights into our financial performance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;em data-stringify-type=&quot;italic&quot;&gt;Their skill set will be invaluable in identifying trends, anomalies, and opportunities that we might otherwise overlook.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol class=&quot;p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__ordered&quot; data-stringify-type=&quot;ordered-list&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Supporting Strategic Initiatives:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;Deep dive into unit economics, using the raw data we have and applying a finance lens to the analysis. The output and conclusions produced will be used as input to our financial model.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol class=&quot;p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__ordered&quot; data-stringify-type=&quot;ordered-list&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
