&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Position Overview:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We‚Äôre looking for a Technical Tribe Lead to join our engineering function. At Xapo, we are building truly cross-functional teams with full ownership of design, architecture, building, testing, delivery, data, and operations. You will lead and collaborate closely with fellow team members from the product, apps, design, and QA communities of practice.&amp;nbsp; You will be part of the Technical Leadership team and will be in charge of all the technical aspects of Xapo Bank products, and your focus will be on Assets Under Management products.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Xapo Bank, we work in Tribes. Each Tribe focuses on a different aspect of providing value to our customers. The Assets Under Management Tribe is in charge of AUM-related products in our app &amp;amp; backoffice domains such as treasury, FinOps, etc. All this responsibility is split across multiple teams, working towards critical KPIs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Technical Tribe Lead, you will provide guidance and coaching around technical good practices and play an active, key role in the Development Community of practice. You will closely lead your dedicated team of Engineers but also be the face of the AUM Tribe (Engineering).&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our main tech stack includes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AWS for all of our Infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Docker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Python (Django, Flask)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MySQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MongoDB&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Redis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We use also:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PostgreSQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Node.js&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Java&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
